    ENDLOOP.

*   ... Or from import parameters
    IF me->upload_parameters IS INITIAL.
      "      APPEND text-027 TO me->log_messages_ref->*.
    ELSE.
      "      APPEND text-026 TO me->log_messages_ref->*.
    ENDIF.

